channel.title: I Code Rsps
channel.description: Kk, i know were all accusing I Code Rsps of RAT'ing servers, but it wasnt him who did it, it was the owner of a server he was on and he was advertising it, not aware of the RAT. Hes a really good friend of mine, and i do have respect for him, and i know he wouldnt do that, ive been coding with him for 2 and a half years now. Just put some thought into it, ive been with moparscape for awhile, i wouldnt put my account on the line for someone if i know there full of shit..
